name: Leo Llama
description: Leo Llama is ruled by the Sun, and that alone demonstrates Leo’s self-confidence. Leo Llama is a born leader; any big project, any group of people, from the latest NFT super collab to the local celestial book club, you’ll find Leo there leading the pride. Leo can be a bit self-centered at times, whether by choice or by accident, taking the spotlight. But the other signs accept this, as his generosity in return is unmatched in the galaxy.
